#1 Layouts (user interface)

Relative Layout:
In relative layout all of our ui element some how related to each other. Its means that the place of every ui element is relative to another layout or its parent.
•	RelativeLayout inside another relative layout.
•	Inside any kind of layout you have relative layout.

Linear Layout:
	UI element will place one after another. You can change orientation
•	Orientation Vertical/Horizontal
•	layout_weight

Constraint layout:
•	constraint 
•	Show Baseline 
•	Helpers > Guidline
•	Set Sample Data (RMB)

